# AB 1889 — Project Context

Website for Akademisk Boldklub (ab.dk). Astro 5 SSR app with Strapi CMS, Sports Innovation API, Descope auth, Mailgun.

## Edit here

- **Active frontend:** `src/` (pages, components, lib, layouts, middleware)
- **CMS:** `strapi/` (separate Yarn process, Strapi v5)
- **Do not edit** `next/` or `astro/` unless explicitly migrating — legacy Next.js / duplicate Astro tree

## Stack

| Layer | Choice |
|---|---|
| Framework | Astro 7, TypeScript strict, `output: 'server'` |
| Adapter | `@astrojs/node` standalone → Docker on datum-cloud |
| UI | Tailwind v4 (`@tailwindcss/vite`) + `src/styles/tokens.css` |
| Interactivity | React islands in `src/components/islands/` only when needed |
| i18n | `da` default (no URL prefix), `en` at `/en/` |

## Commands

```bash
npm install && npm run dev    # http://localhost:4321
npm run check                 # TypeScript + Astro diagnostics
npm run build                 # verify before PR
npm run format:check          # Prettier
cd strapi && yarn develop     # CMS at :1337 (needs Postgres or sqlite)
```

## Env

Copy `.env.example` → `.env.local`. Minimum: `STRAPI_URL`, `STRAPI_API_TOKEN`. Never commit secrets.

## Verification

- Run `npm run build` after non-trivial changes
- Health check: `GET /api/health` → `{"ok":true}`
